    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p local-id=\"b6e1b638855a\" /><p local-id=\"7e767bfc6226\" /><h3 local-id=\"369b700d39f6\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-LoadthePlug-in\">Load the Plug-in</h3><p local-id=\"a3de7f5f6bd6\">Open the Plug-in Manager in Maya, scroll down and find the RenderMan for Maya plug-in.  If you can't find RenderMan for Maya listed, <em>don't</em> head for the browse button.  See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544538696/Installation+of+RenderMan+for+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538696\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">troubleshooting</a> to figure out what may have gone wrong during installation.</p><p local-id=\"8ef1c9bcc206\"><strong>Windows &gt; Settings/Preferences &gt; Plug-In Manager</strong></p><p local-id=\"5806aad1e2f5\"><strong> </strong><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedOine.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=667&amp;height=438\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedOine.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"438\" data-width=\"667\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538768\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedOine.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"79853364-d390-4cfa-8fd1-21b65c321ae4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedOine.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=667&amp;height=438 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedOine.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=667&amp;height=438 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"da8c287e2526\"><br/><br/>After the RenderMan for Maya plug-in has been successfully loaded, the first thing you should notice is the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544538944/RenderMan+Shelf\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538944\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Shelf</a>, which will be available each time Maya starts, even before the plug-in is loaded.</p><p local-id=\"ee23c1c798da\" /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_Shelf.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=30\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/RenderMan_Shelf.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"39\" data-width=\"882\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538765\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Shelf.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"7272849f-17ae-4287-92ac-2d8cf214881b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_Shelf.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=882&amp;height=39 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_Shelf.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=30 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"b71be0423e32\"><br/><br/>The shelf includes a button that loads the plug-in.<br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfLoadPlugin.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmShelfLoadPlugin.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538831\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfLoadPlugin.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"ebca19e6-db40-40fc-964c-cf75a2719f19\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfLoadPlugin.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfLoadPlugin.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-local-id=\"4a5ea92ce6db\" data-macro-id=\"dfc85bf4-5fe2-4edb-8834-3d4a21a0a269\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p local-id=\"a840587149ae\">Note, unloading and then reloading the RenderMan for Maya plug-in is not expected to work. You’ll need to restart Maya if you want to re-load the plugin.</p></div></div><h3 local-id=\"91f83f0710bd\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-PreferredRenderer\">Preferred Renderer</h3><p local-id=\"7340d9ef32e2\">The first time RenderMan for Maya is loaded, a dialog will ask if you would like RenderMan to be your preferred renderer.  This simply sets the Maya preference for the preferred renderer.  Each time a new scene is created in Maya, the preferred renderer becomes active.<br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPreferredRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=360&amp;height=113\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmPreferredRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"113\" data-width=\"360\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538777\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmPreferredRenderer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"981121dd-ae21-4761-a15b-77bb184d5844\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPreferredRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=360&amp;height=113 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPreferredRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=360&amp;height=113 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"fd253306aa69\"><br/><br/></p><p local-id=\"66abc245b14c\">If RenderMan is not set as your preferred renderer, any of the RenderMan shelf buttons will switch back to RenderMan before performing their action, or you can switch in the Render Settings.<br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSelectRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533983&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=464&amp;height=911\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmSelectRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533983&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"911\" data-width=\"464\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538771\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmSelectRenderer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"64263f6b-c86d-45c4-b109-e2456f1ece60\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSelectRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533983&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=464&amp;height=911 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSelectRenderer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533983&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=464&amp;height=911 1x\"></span><hr local-id=\"a3479afd60ce\"/><h3 local-id=\"f586465b3223\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-Let&#39;sRenderSomething!\">Let's Render Something!</h3><p local-id=\"6f78423d409f\">RenderMan for Maya requires RenderMan lights and materials.  Most of Maya's texture nodes are <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539520/Supported+Maya+Nodes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539520\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">supported</a>, but Maya lights and materials are ignored.</p><p local-id=\"c11e7b039830\" /><h4 local-id=\"46c1d6bb53a0\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-SetUpLights\">Set Up Lights</h4><p local-id=\"a5f570d67f02\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661727/Lighting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661727\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan lights</a> can be created via the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544538944/RenderMan+Shelf\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538944\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Shelf</a>, Hypershade, or the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539259/RenderMan+Menu\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539259\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Menu</a>.</p><p local-id=\"92dab26b2d95\">Go ahead and create a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661749/PxrEnvDayLight\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661749\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrEnvDayLight</a> using the shelf button's popup menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmCreateDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=94\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmCreateDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"94\" data-width=\"217\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538783\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmCreateDayLight.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"cf729204-057f-4f8e-9cf5-8da11bae33b9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmCreateDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=94 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmCreateDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=94 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"ffeee81d7976\">You'll see a new light manipulator in the scene:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"679\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=272\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmEnvDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"272\" data-width=\"453\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538786\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmEnvDayLight.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"62865acc-93b9-4bfc-b929-662c66c7851a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=272 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534222&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=272 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"425a5ce035a3\">Hitting the 't' key while the manipulator is selected allows you to interactively position the sun.  Other RenderMan lights show a center of interest manipulator when you hit 't'.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLightT.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=351\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmEnvDayLightT.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"351\" data-width=\"453\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538789\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmEnvDayLightT.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"edafb28b-b7f9-4b98-9962-bedf8a1a8e10\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLightT.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=351 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmEnvDayLightT.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=453&amp;height=351 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"30ef5ab81201\">A couple of commonly adjusted controls on RenderMan lights are exposure and visibility.  Lights have a physical falloff.  If a light seems dark in a scene, you may want to turn up the exposure from 0.  Increasing by 1 doubles the energy emitted by the light source.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightExposure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=422&amp;height=81\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmLightExposure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"81\" data-width=\"422\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538801\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmLightExposure.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f667a884-fff6-452d-9dcd-14831d663592\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightExposure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=422&amp;height=81 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightExposure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=422&amp;height=81 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"0386416c7368\">By default, lights are not visible to the camera, so if you want to see the color of the daylight in the background, it needs to be made visible to the camera.<br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightVisibility.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=521\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmLightVisibility.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"521\" data-width=\"482\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538816\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmLightVisibility.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"0f9e0be4-8a20-43f9-a3b6-a781b95bcd79\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightVisibility.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=521 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmLightVisibility.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=521 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"c73b39847559\">Even if you do not create any RenderMan lights or materials in your scene, the render will not be black, as long as Maya's default light setting is enabled in the Render Settings.  Any Maya materials will render with the default RenderMan PxrDiffuse shader, which looks a lot like Maya's default lambert.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"672\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmDefaultLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=462&amp;height=785\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmDefaultLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"785\" data-width=\"462\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538813\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmDefaultLight.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"43b42156-043c-470b-a0f9-33f7a6faf95b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmDefaultLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=462&amp;height=785 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmDefaultLight.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=462&amp;height=785 1x\"></span><h4 local-id=\"d3a85c57600a\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-CreateGeometry\">Create Geometry</h4><p local-id=\"2b81a9121216\">Let's create a polygon sphere, from Maya's Polygons shelf.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSphere.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmSphere.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538834\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmSphere.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"30d4083f-0ad9-4978-8c3e-c80826ca6a20\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSphere.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmSphere.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><h4 local-id=\"92d8e2cb5602\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-SetUpMaterials\">Set Up Materials</h4><p local-id=\"787e18a644f7\">The RenderMan shelf has a button which creates a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661415/PxrSurface\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661415\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrSurface</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661463/PxrLayerSurface\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661463\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrLayerSurface</a> and attaches to the current selection.  Legacy materials, like PxrDisney are available through the RenderMan section in the Hypershade window.</p><p local-id=\"0b5ef6c473bb\">Select the sphere in your scene and click the PxrSurface button.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmShelfSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538837\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfSurface.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"ebd6c07d-d398-4165-84cb-32d0986aa655\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535516&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><h4 local-id=\"916f068e6b97\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-Patterns\">Patterns</h4><p local-id=\"dba1b0b14925\">Attributes of PxrSurface can be connected to most <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539520/Supported+Maya+Nodes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539520\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Maya texture nodes</a> or any of RenderMan's extensive set of <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661575/Patterns\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661575\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">pattern</a> nodes.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=357&amp;height=634\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"634\" data-width=\"357\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538762\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedTwo.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"603b5ef4-317d-4b70-a805-423c4f7230be\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=357&amp;height=634 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/RenderMan_RfM_GettingStartedTwo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431533738&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=357&amp;height=634 1x\"></span><h4 local-id=\"6e6908b9aa6e\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-PresetBrowser\">Preset Browser</h4><p local-id=\"970e7eb5c35a\">PxrSurface is the single material that you can go to for nearly all your shading needs.  But that one we just created actually looks pretty dull. And the list of attributes looks a bit daunting.  Where to start?  RenderMan includes a library of preset material networks based on PxrSurface.</p><p local-id=\"82129d9ece23\">Let's check it out!  Click this button in the RenderMan shelf to open the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539564/Preset+Browser+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539564\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Preset Browser</a>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmShelfPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfPresetBrowser.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"c1258f97-69ad-4a9f-81bc-88c3be7042fb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"e7c50ef5f3a3\">The first time you open the Preset Browser, a file dialog will open asking you to navigate to the location of a preset library.  The one that ships with RenderMan is under the install.</p><p local-id=\"d20895948b6a\">eg.  <strong>C:/Program Files/Pixar/RenderManProServer-24.0/lib/RenderManAssetLibrary</strong></p><p local-id=\"0392d675c308\">Either copy that directory to your own work area and point there, or go ahead and point the preset browser at the one in the install.</p><p local-id=\"37ca96890e87\">If you ever need to change this location, visit the Preset Browser section of the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539308/RenderMan+Preferences\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539308\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Preferences</a>.</p><p local-id=\"fbceaf31a928\">Here's how the Preset Browser will look once it finds the presets, and you click on one of the categories.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"533\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=822\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"822\" data-width=\"412\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538795\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmPresetBrowser.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f511a79f-b74f-47c6-9b1c-7ca890d58721\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=822 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmPresetBrowser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=822 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"1e790763d038\">Right-click on a material to import and attach it to selected geometry.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"672\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmImportCopper.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=311&amp;height=172\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmImportCopper.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"172\" data-width=\"311\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538798\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmImportCopper.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"23d1c579-d9d3-4d61-8968-872a1b88caf0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmImportCopper.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=311&amp;height=172 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmImportCopper.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=311&amp;height=172 1x\"></span><h4 local-id=\"0a5e3626333a\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-Render!\">Render!</h4><p local-id=\"8fe2ac722b03\">The RenderMan shelf includes buttons for preview rendering and <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661821/Interactive+Rendering\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661821\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">interactive preview rendering</a> (IPR).  Maya's buttons for these actions work as well.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPreview.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmShelfPreview.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538846\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfPreview.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"05d6ff0c-cebe-41cb-8b5c-1e506f3a78fe\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPreview.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfPreview.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfIPR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmShelfIPR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538849\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfIPR.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f53c1c71-1fb8-4eff-95a2-cedc4d64fbb5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfIPR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmShelfIPR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"70aa3260e495\">IPR continues rendering until stopped, while changes to materials or lights appear in the render.  Preview rendering continues until the image converges or is cancelled.</p><p local-id=\"f74245592cbc\">The first time you render, the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661909/Image+Tool\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661909\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Image Tool</a> 'It' opens.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"679\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=679&amp;height=363\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmItRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"433\" data-width=\"809\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538804\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmItRender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"62ada4c6-f330-4508-81b6-66256dcf6cbe\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=809&amp;height=433 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=679&amp;height=363 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"880c83dd8460\">The Image Tool has a button that will cancel either preview or IPR renders.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItCancel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=33&amp;height=31\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmItCancel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"31\" data-width=\"33\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538807\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmItCancel.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"0663a16d-1905-4dc7-a7da-df444164ed0b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItCancel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=33&amp;height=31 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItCancel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=33&amp;height=31 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"8b52d8091345\">You can also use the &quot;escape&quot; hot-key to easily cancel renders from the Image Tool window.</p><p local-id=\"1aed79c9c604\">If you prefer to use Maya's Render View, visit the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539308/RenderMan+Preferences\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539308\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Preferences</a>.</p><h4 local-id=\"17c42e6fdb07\" id=\"GettingStartedinMaya-RenderSettings\">Render Settings</h4><p local-id=\"1ae607c2febc\">You'll get a reasonable render out of the box without adjusting <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544542282/Render+Settings+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542282\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Render Settings</a>.  However, let's take a look at a few of the interesting things that can be accessed there.</p><p local-id=\"2d64cd823a0c\" /><p local-id=\"158de390722b\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"260\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsFeatures.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=260&amp;height=471\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsFeatures.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538822\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmRenderSettingsFeatures.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"18e7ce66-ec9b-4186-8cd8-489f5f02d534\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsFeatures.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=441&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsFeatures.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=260&amp;height=471 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"260\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsPasses.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=260&amp;height=471\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsPasses.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538819\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmRenderSettingsPasses.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3bb66739-69fd-4ed4-bf1e-a8d76a86c531\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsPasses.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=441&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmRenderSettingsPasses.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431535157&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=260&amp;height=471 1x\"></span><br/></p><ul local-id=\"7c62ae442d9b\"><li local-id=\"ba7b8155ab88\"><p local-id=\"451be84e6873\">The Path Tracer is the default integrator, but you can try out others, even while IPR is running.  </p></li><li local-id=\"708aeea2920c\"><p local-id=\"245d604233b2\">Enable features like <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544541742/Motion+Blur+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541742\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">motion blur</a> and denoise.</p></li><li local-id=\"379d09fb0ac2\"><p local-id=\"3083ff72c5e4\">Add extra <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661871/Arbitrary+Output+Variables\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661871\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Outputs</a> to the render.  These get written out at the same time as the main render and can be viewed in the Image Tool</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"828\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItAOVs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=809&amp;height=434\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538718/rfmItAOVs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"434\" data-width=\"809\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538810\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmItAOVs.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538718\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"92318933-0bd9-4841-a0af-68b2c3100908\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItAOVs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=809&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538718/rfmItAOVs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431534910&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=809&amp;height=434 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"fd1f16d7ca9a\" />"
